      "content": "but i dont think i want to keep walking. there's this feeling that the trip has served its purpose, you know? like if you keep traveling after you've seen the main sights, you're just wandering aimlessly. sometimes a journey needs a proper conclusion so it doesn't just fade into nothing.",
